## Component Development Checklist

When creating or modifying components, ensure they:
0. ✅ Write simple, organizized code, using best practices.
1. ✅ Follow mobile-first design principles
2. ✅ Use app constants for colors, spacing, typography, and border radius
3. ✅ Implement responsive behavior using the responsive system
4. ✅ Handle vertical tab bar spacing on large screens
5. ✅ Keep all styles in style hooks, not in component render methods
6. ✅ Use proper shadow implementation for cross-platform compatibility
7. ✅ Apply proper spacing using margin/padding best practices
8. ✅ Support internationalization
9. ✅ Are tested on multiple screen sizes and platforms 

10. ✅ Make sure to use the shadow utilities when using shadows.
11. ✅ Make sure to use ternary over conditional in the return function when rendering jsx components.






